“How about this” – she wets her lips with a quick lick of her tongue “You’re in a ship housing four of the most dangerous mercenaries on the galaxy” – Ooookay… “Each of whom can kill without remorse” – Alright “Now what would happen if they saw a stranger messi-“

“I see where you’re getting at” – You interrupt her explanation. Yeah, it wouldn’t be very fun to one minute be fixing a ship and the next having your ghost futilely trying to collect the remains of your head against the ship’s hull. 

