Wolf guides you through the aforementioned corridor and as you follow, you take the time to take a good look at your boring surroundings. You know you’ve said before, but it really has to be said again, the inside really doesn’t give the ship’s outward appearance any justice. Only this time instead of a dirty and busted up hangar you get a boring set of hallways with boring blast doors and built with boring steel in the color of a boring gray.

