“Oh, definitely” – She agrees with an exasperated sigh “I don’t think I’d stand another day with him snorting on my ears for a mechanic” – Wolf then looks up to you with curiosity in her eyes “Anyway, speaking of star fighters, what is yours anyway?”

You lean back a little in surprise, eyes widening a bit from the out of a sudden question. 

