“Because I modded it, of course” – You puff your chest in pride, that ship is one of your greatest achievements. You made it pretty much indistinguishable from an Arwing from the outside, and even some of the inside too.

“You, an entire ship?” – She sneers condescendingly “When you’re having so much trouble with mine?”

