Remember one of her quirks? She has so many of them that it is honeslty hard to keep track, but narrowing it down to the day you met her gives you. You think some more, and watch her drink down the beer, trying to remember what it is she wants you to remember. By the time your answer finally comes up, she’s already finished with that beer and have already reached for the last one.

